headline: OPW Retail Fueling Unveils 68EZSB Reconnectable Swivel Breakaway
summary: OPW Retail Fueling, part of Dover (NYSE: DOV) and a global leader in fluid-handling solutions, today announced the launch of the 68EZSB Reconnectable Swivel Breakaway. The next generation 68EZSB features a compact, lightweight design that incorporates 360ยบ swivel rotation at both the male end and middle joint, with an easily reconnectable breakaway on the opposite end.
